title: Pixel 3 XL won't connect to 5g wifi
content: I have a Pixel 3 XL and I have 5g wifi at my house and one morning I woke up and my phone was dead I went to plug it in and turned it on and I wasn't connected to my 5g wifi I would say "connecting" then right after it was say "saved".
category: Connectivity, Network, Bluetooth, Google Pixel 3 XL
